{
  "text": "In this section we describe a method, improved and augmented from [CITATION_1] , to transform the Functional Representation of CEs into its referential counterpart, also named Calendar Intervals (CI). This step is useful to perform similarity comparisons between several CEs.",
  "citation_candidates": [
